    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. Mechanically, it is very sound, providing a smooth and reliable driving experience with all major systems functioning as they should. The interior is clean and shows only minimal wear, while the exterior remains attractive despite some minor stone chips and light surface scratches consistent with careful regular use. It\u2019s a solid, dependable car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
