    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking for a new home for my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for everything from grocery runs to weekend road trips. It still looks great and runs like a dream! If you're looking for a dependable car that\u2019s been well-loved and is ready for many more miles, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message if you want to come take a look!",
      "price": 31800.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
