    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and Double VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, ensuring direct engagement with the factory-spec limited-slip differential. To ensure structural and internal longevity, the rear subframe has been reinforced and the rod bearings have been replaced with treated shells. The chassis maintains its poise via MacPherson struts and a multi-link rear suspension, providing the precise lateral feedback expected of the M-chassis. While the exterior shows honest signs of use, the mechanical synchronization and throttle calibration remain razor-sharp, making this an ideal specimen for the purist driver.",
